{"tid":2494181,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[ViuTV] Chill Club年度推介20/21 星期日 20:00 (14) 人人樂壇 音樂第一","createTime":"2021-04-18T12:42:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T13:53:21.000Z","uid":170666,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"b2789847a5dd474e4ffe39730dbf77eddabe0748","tid":2494181,"uid":170666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T12:42:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nc8rB9n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnc8rB9n.jpg&h=c81660b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nChill Club 推介榜年度推介20/21<br />\n香港ViuTV主辦的首屆本地流行音樂頒獎典禮，於2021年4月18日晚上8時假九龍灣國際展貿中心E-Max匯星舉行，由趙學而、駱振偉擔任司儀，主題爲「人人樂壇，音樂第一」，評選範圍爲2020年5月31日（2020年第22週）至2021年2月28日（2021年第9週）「Chill Club 推介榜」的上榜歌曲及歌手。除幕後獎項外，各大獎項均由全港市民一人一票投票產生。<br />\n本次頒獎典禮由「FWD富衛保險」冠名贊助。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8iiWeV2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8iiWeV2.jpg&h=5147031a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RZNv3Pn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRZNv3Pn.jpg&h=5b3cdc25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6LAEW9n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6LAEW9n.jpg&h=317f8489&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6932ae392785fcff1c689d5d887f3a8cf8485bdb","tid":2494181,"uid":1230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T13:22:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea805fd9d53e0ed2cb0b9d0778ada32461f4a1cf","tid":2494181,"uid":235277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T13:24:07.000Z","msg":"咁就14<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d41f3ab69cf8c6c618e97f56bf1c6fafe2915c8","tid":2494181,"uid":360082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T13:32:43.000Z","msg":"有冇人開15？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"